name: Postcard from Cok City
description: The city of Surabaya does have many stories of the struggle of the youth for Indonesian independence.  One of the most memorable is the heroic action of the arek-arek Suroboyo, as the people of Surabaya are called, in the battle of 10 November 1945. ... Thanks to that incident, the city of Surabaya was also known as the City of Heroes and Hot city
